<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="es">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8" />
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
  <title>Maquila | Inventario de Productos</title>
  <link href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.3.3/dist/css/bootstrap.min.css" rel="stylesheet">
  <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Roboto:wght@300;500;700&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
  <link href="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/font-awesome/6.0.0-beta3/css/all.min.css" rel="stylesheet">


  <style>
    body {
      font-family: 'Segoe UI', Tahoma, Geneva, Verdana, sans-serif;
      background: linear-gradient(135deg, #0a1d56, #0d1b2a);
      color: #343a40;
    }

    header {
      background: linear-gradient(to right, #1a237e, #3949ab);
      padding: 20px 0;
      text-align: center;
      color: white;
      box-shadow: 0 2px 8px rgba(0,0,0,0.2);
    }

    .section-title {
      font-weight: 700;
      margin-bottom: 20px;
    }

    .table-section {
      background: linear-gradient(135deg, #f3f4f7, #ffffff);
      border-radius: 16px;
      box-shadow: 0 0 15px rgba(0,0,0,0.05);
      padding: 25px;
    }

    .table thead {
      background-color: #1a237e;
      color: white;
    }

    .table td, .table th {
      vertical-align: middle;
    }

    .btn-success {
      background: linear-gradient(to right, #2e7d32, #388e3c);
      border: none;
    }

    .btn-info {
      background: linear-gradient(to right, #039be5, #0288d1);
      border: none;
    }

    .btn-danger {
      background: linear-gradient(to right, #d32f2f, #c62828);
      border: none;
    }

    .card {
      border: none;
      border-radius: 16px;
      box-shadow: 0 0 15px rgba(0,0,0,0.05);
    }

    .card-header {
      background: linear-gradient(to right, #3949ab, #5c6bc0);
      border-top-left-radius: 16px;
      border-top-right-radius: 16px;
      color: white;
    }

    .form-control:focus {
      border-color: #1a237e;
      box-shadow: 0 0 5px rgba(26, 35, 126, 0.5);
    }

    .hero-section {
      background: linear-gradient(to right, #1a237e, #3949ab);
      color: white;
      padding: 60px 0;
      text-align: center;
      border-radius: 16px;
      margin: 60px 0 30px;
      box-shadow: 0 4px 20px rgba(0,0,0,0.2);
    }

    .hero-section img {
      max-width: 600px;
      width: 100%;
      height: auto;
      margin-top: 20px;
      border-radius: 12px;
      box-shadow: 0 4px 20px rgba(0,0,0,0.3);
    }

    .content-section {
      padding: 60px 0;
      background: linear-gradient(135deg, #ffffff, #f8f9fb);
      border-top: 5px solid #1a237e;
      border-radius: 12px;
      box-shadow: 0 4px 15px rgba(0,0,0,0.05);
    }
  </style>
</head>

<body>
<header>
  <h1>Inventario de Productos</h1>

  <p class="lead mb-0"><%= data.length > 0 ? 'Mostrando productos disponibles' : 'No hay datos disponibles' %></p>
</header>

<div class="container my-5">
  <a href="/home" class="btn btn-primary">
    <i class="fa-solid fa-circle-arrow-left"></i></i> Regresar
  </a>

  <div class="row">
    <div class="col-lg-8 mb-4">
      <div class="table-section">
        <h3 class="section-title">Lista de Productos</h3>
        <div class="table-responsive">
          <table class="table table-striped table-hover">
            <thead>
              <tr>
                <th>No.</th>
                <th>ID del Producto</th>
                <th>Nombre</th>
                <th>Descripción</th>
                <th>Categoría</th>
                <th>Unidad</th>
                <th>Proveedor</th>
                <th>Código QR</th>
                <th>Acciones</th>
              </tr>
            </thead>
            <tbody>
              <% if (data.length > 0) { %>
                <% for (var i = 0; i < data.length; i++) { %>
                  <tr>
                    <td><%= i + 1 %></td>
                    <td><%= data[i].idProduct %></td>
                    <td><%= data[i].name %></td>
                    <td><%= data[i].description %></td>
                    <td><%= data[i].category %></td>
                    <td><%= data[i].unitof %></td>
                    <td><%= data[i].supplier %></td>
                    <td><%= data[i].barcode %></td>
                    <td>
                      <a href="/inventario/delete/<%= data[i].id %>" class="btn btn-danger btn-sm">Eliminar</a>
                      <a href="/inventario/update/<%= data[i].id %>" class="btn btn-info btn-sm">Actualizar</a>
                    </td>
                  </tr>
                <% } %>
              <% } else { %>
                <tr><td colspan="9" class="text-center">No hay datos disponibles</td></tr>
              <% } %>
            </tbody>
          </table>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="col-lg-4">
      <div class="card">
        <div class="card-header">
          <h5 class="mb-0">Agregar Nuevo Producto</h5>
        </div>
        <div class="card-body">
          <form action="/inventario/add" method="post">
            <div class="mb-3">
              <label for="idProduct" class="form-label">ID del Producto</label>
              <input type="text" name="idProduct" id="idProduct" class="form-control" required>
            </div>
            <div class="mb-3">
              <label for="name" class="form-label">Nombre del Producto</label>
              <input type="text" name="name" id="name" class="form-control" required>
            </div>
            <div class="mb-3">
              <label for="description" class="form-label">Descripción</label>
              <input type="text" name="description" id="description" class="form-control" required>
            </div>
            <div class="mb-3">
              <label for="category" class="form-label">Categoría</label>
              <input type="text" name="category" id="category" class="form-control" required>
            </div>
            <div class="mb-3">
              <label for="unitof" class="form-label">Unidad de Medida</label>
              <input type="text" name="unitof" id="unitof" class="form-control" required>
            </div>
            <div class="mb-3">
              <label for="supplier" class="form-label">Proveedor</label>
              <input type="text" name="supplier" id="supplier" class="form-control" required>
            </div>
            <div class="mb-3">
              <label for="barcode" class="form-label">Código QR</label>
              <input type="text" name="barcode" id="barcode" class="form-control" required>
            </div>
            <button type="submit" class="btn btn-success w-100">Guardar en Inventario</button>
          </form>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>

<section class="hero-section">
  <div class="container">
    <p class="lead">Tu socio confiable en la industria de maquila</p>
    <img src="/Imagen1.png" alt="Imagen de Maquila" class="img-fluid">
  </div>
</section>

<section class="content-section">
  <div class="container">
    <h2 class="text-center mb-4">Acerca de Maquila</h2>
    <p class="text-center px-md-5">
      Ofrecemos soluciones de vanguardia para optimizar el proceso de maquila.
      Nuestro enfoque está en la calidad, eficiencia y satisfacción del cliente.
      Únete a nosotros para ampliar tu capacidad de producción con los mejores servicios de la industria.
    </p>
  </div>
</section>

<script src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.3.3/dist/js/bootstrap.bundle.min.js"></script>
</body>
</html>
